buyGDFromReserve(uint256,uint256).details: buy GD from reserve using ETH since reserve  is in cDAI we first buy DAI from uniswap -> mint cDAI -> buy GD

params.minDAIAmount: - the min amount of DAI to receive for buying with ETH
params.minGDAmount: - the min amount of GD to receive for buying with cDAI(via DAI)

buyGDFromUniswap(uint256).details: buy GD from uniswap pool using ETH since pool is in DAI we first buy DAI from uniswap -> buy GD

params.minGDAmount: - the min amount of GD to receive for buying with DAI(via ETH)

sellGDFromReserveToUniswap(uint256,uint2.details: buy GD from reserve using ETH and sell to uniswap pool resulting in DAI

params.minDAIAmount: - the min amount of dai to receive for selling G$
params.minGDAmount: - the min amount of GD to receive for buying with cDAI(via ETH)
